{"tid":102560,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"去完以色列 你問我答","createTime":"2017-01-31T17:09:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-02T15:06:59.000Z","uid":56757,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f6bff51a9705194a3d3db0fa4749747ece9bd680","tid":102560,"uid":56757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T17:09:05.000Z","msg":"啱啱去完以色列十幾日，快手快腳咁去過Tel Aviv, Haifa同埋Jerusalem<br />\n<br />\n先附上一張地中海靚相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fH2UW4T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfH2UW4T.png&h=b33012b1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7fedc730f5e2c1b8b34b8b1efb4172bca903b984","tid":102560,"uid":11323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T17:12:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啱啱去完以色列十幾日，快手快腳咁去過Tel Aviv, Haifa同埋Jerusalem<br />\n<br />\n先附上一張地中海靚相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fH2UW4T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfH2UW4T.png&h=b33012b1&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n搭邊間airline 同埋住邊到好 仲有成個trip用左幾錢<br />\n<br />\n唔該樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb2b5e21261078ecff6fd1f96e0f10eea5bb9562","tid":102560,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T17:20:39.000Z","msg":"有冇叫雞"},{"pid":"cfa6f0c3a0452f6e225080c055902edc78c6122b","tid":102560,"uid":56757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T17:36:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>啱啱去完以色列十幾日，快手快腳咁去過Tel Aviv, Haifa同埋Jerusalem<br />\n<br />\n先附上一張地中海靚相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fH2UW4T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfH2UW4T.png&h=b33012b1&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n搭邊間airline 同埋住邊到好 仲有成個trip用左幾錢<br />\n<br />\n唔該樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我自己就搭以色列航空去嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />去程嘅時候成架機都滿左逼到瞓唔到，回程嘅時候就冇人到可以一個人瞓兩個位<br />\nBtw因為我係搭直航機去特拉維夫所以先揀以色列航空<br />\n基本上以色列洗費都幾高下，你預一個午餐都差唔多80港紙到<br />\n我就住四星級左右嘅酒店都要差唔到$400美元雙人房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28efaa5a9eb59d1cb2523521b2484e6279f97b16","tid":102560,"uid":56757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T17:36:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇叫雞</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecbf8ec880cfa340b02ee46a835d28d6561b78aa","tid":102560,"uid":73923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T17:47:15.000Z","msg":"覺得啲當地人點"},{"pid":"59473c86ac2b31610c8f2453ce09dfe0e777618f","tid":102560,"uid":56757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T17:50:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>覺得啲當地人點</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一般以色列猶太人都幾熱情下，行過見到你亞洲人面孔都會撩下你傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ea1666e34fcc0698c37b7a209077224d8b4bf9f","tid":102560,"uid":73923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T17:54:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>覺得啲當地人點</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一般以色列猶太人都幾熱情下，行過見到你亞洲人面孔都會撩下你傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪好撚多靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"853b313be65c6ee9e6e730275042e7aff90f6563","tid":102560,"uid":56757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T17:58:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>覺得啲當地人點</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一般以色列猶太人都幾熱情下，行過見到你亞洲人面孔都會撩下你傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪好撚多靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n靚女仲多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為當年立國嘅時候有一半係歐洲各地嘅人一半係阿拉伯猶太人所以mix出嚟個個都係好有特性"},{"pid":"cb3e7c6d0108582cb73379a430503c9da44fde6b","tid":102560,"uid":31905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T18:00:16.000Z","msg":"唔驚有炸彈？"},{"pid":"e8cac9333643b17ec33899b5416a6bf39a072289","tid":102560,"uid":858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T18:04:16.000Z","msg":"以色列航空嘅航機係咪真係會有個陀槍嘅特警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9da2d639b2f9781b753546b5d988e3fb0e0d38b","tid":102560,"uid":74728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T18:05:58.000Z","msg":"係唔係個個都猶太教，安息日係唔係連lift都唔按層層停？"},{"pid":"a4ed1c5a42bba074c7348974760dcdb4ab7ca8b1","tid":102560,"uid":56757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T18:25:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔驚有炸彈？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實大部分嘅地方都好安全，係近西岸同埋耶路撒冷會比較緊張少少，但係一般嚟講好少會搞到遊客"},{"pid":"357265699ddce8bcb9bb886a327f7ed7f6fc2f1c","tid":102560,"uid":56757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T18:26:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以色列航空嘅航機係咪真係會有個陀槍嘅特警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n是沒有的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過會有啲好高嘅空少同埋架機好似係防導彈嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75aa9ed08c83058b8f490604d588803cbde9e768","tid":102560,"uid":56757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T18:30:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係唔係個個都猶太教，安息日係唔係連lift都唔按層層停？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n相得比較足個啲係唔掂得機械，記得啱啱踏入安息日嘅淩晨十二點幾嘅時候有對猶太母女行入嚟部到，想㩒掣個下即刻縮手，跟住我就主動幫佢地㩒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n正常安息日係有一部會自動層層停唔洗㩒掣嘅"},{"pid":"b4fb8ced26ffce453a6d77ab295f029ef4ef70a7","tid":102560,"uid":858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T23:48:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>以色列航空嘅航機係咪真係會有個陀槍嘅特警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n是沒有的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過會有啲好高嘅空少同埋架機好似係防導彈嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所有以色列航空的飛行員都曾經是以色列空軍的飛行員，而且都受過搏擊訓練。也因為由於以色列是個強制服兵役的國家的關係，所有以色列航空的僱員均曾經在以色列陸軍服役。<span style=\"color: red;\">每班國際航班都有最少6名攜有槍械的特工偽裝成乘客（實際數量因屬以色列保安資料，政府和航空公司沒有公開）</span>，其機隊也配備了反導彈裝備，此外以色列航空在海外機場停留時，會有手持長槍的機場特警在停機坪駐守及巡邏。 <br />\n<br />\n定係其實有 但你唔知咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"481968440f1af3135a35dada390eef35ec882224","tid":102560,"uid":51268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T00:01:10.000Z","msg":"過關出境同入境煩唔煩？<br />\n有冇去巴勒斯坦？"},{"pid":"fbfd50c326c5e287ad1a03f18ce9feea2de3d73b","tid":102560,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T01:24:57.000Z","msg":"我本護照去過d回教國家，係唔係唔洗去？"},{"pid":"da9f513d043450e633e541c0aefaceb81be41e45","tid":102560,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T01:38:53.000Z","msg":"剩係以色列十幾日？無落約旦？<br />\n<br />\n交通樓主唔會豪到出入都的士卦？"},{"pid":"fd5fca4c086d8149e413ad84dd700e1a95ec99f9","tid":102560,"uid":56757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T05:33:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>以色列航空嘅航機係咪真係會有個陀槍嘅特警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n是沒有的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過會有啲好高嘅空少同埋架機好似係防導彈嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所有以色列航空的飛行員都曾經是以色列空軍的飛行員，而且都受過搏擊訓練。也因為由於以色列是個強制服兵役的國家的關係，所有以色列航空的僱員均曾經在以色列陸軍服役。<span style=\"color: red;\">每班國際航班都有最少6名攜有槍械的特工偽裝成乘客（實際數量因屬以色列保安資料，政府和航空公司沒有公開）</span>，其機隊也配備了反導彈裝備，此外以色列航空在海外機場停留時，會有手持長槍的機場特警在停機坪駐守及巡邏。 <br />\n<br />\n定係其實有 但你唔知咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能有但係我地同差唔多全班機嘅人都傾過計，可能其中幾個就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3078c45a804ef7d6f14321f969a27ae28541d60","tid":102560,"uid":56757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T05:36:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>過關出境同入境煩唔煩？<br />\n有冇去巴勒斯坦？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係香港上機個時會好似查家宅咁問你好多問題，例如問你去做咩，有冇幫人攞野(最好答冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />答有可能會叫你開行李)"},{"pid":"1f8571435f37d0755c975e4d469942310ed14187","tid":102560,"uid":56757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T05:37:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我本護照去過d回教國家，係唔係唔洗去？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同行有回教國家嘅同學連visa都唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad5d425791cdd3a08dc474441632185bdf7fb768","tid":102560,"uid":56757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T05:37:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>剩係以色列十幾日？無落約旦？<br />\n<br />\n交通樓主唔會豪到出入都的士卦？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實是跟團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd8e1244d9bce0da518946676d537c8e14463410","tid":102560,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T05:40:16.000Z","msg":"需唔需要希伯來文?"},{"pid":"72f7d033a87d8090c17298e8ea6ba0a7de00dd55","tid":102560,"uid":56757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T05:43:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>需唔需要希伯來文?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同香港差唔多，遊客區比較多人識英文，後生啲嘅會多啲識英文，中老年英文識得個一兩句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過去之前識番一兩句Shalom,Toda會幾impress到當地人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d363c011e51b52f05f47cf9ca8f22b0b5bde756","tid":102560,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T05:48:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>剩係以色列十幾日？無落約旦？<br />\n<br />\n交通樓主唔會豪到出入都的士卦？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實是跟團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即係齋聖地遊蹤？<br />\n<br />\n宗教團？"},{"pid":"acf1290723d6c4aeb62fbd329222aba4896ac32e","tid":102560,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T05:49:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我本護照去過d回教國家，係唔係唔洗去？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同行有回教國家嘅同學連visa都唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我準備挑機<br />\n<br />\n去完馬來西亞先再去以色列。(前後唔夠2個月)"},{"pid":"2fdaee48ebacd11f3c17be8e34386b1347236efa","tid":102560,"uid":38461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T05:50:27.000Z","msg":"依家有cx直航<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aff93dab412b6072025488a51930e0998ff0756a","tid":102560,"uid":38461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T05:51:44.000Z","msg":"樓主不如post下相同行程<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d64caf15cf5c9a240f050026a5a352967fcaa5d7","tid":102560,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T05:53:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我本護照去過d回教國家，係唔係唔洗去？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同行有回教國家嘅同學連visa都唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 