00Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我本護照去過d回教國家，係唔係唔洗去？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同行有回教國家嘅同學連visa都唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我準備挑機<br />\n<br />\n去完馬來西亞先再去以色列。(前後唔夠2個月)</blockquote><br />\n馬拉都計?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n回教國家<br />\n<br />\n馬拉人話佢地本護照寫明唔准去以色列。 (睇其他地方講)<br />\n<br />\n不過一樣有人會去到。</blockquote><br />\n馬拉護照寫到明「本護照於各國有效，以色列除外。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/lcwfmoqs\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Flcwfmoqs&h=b845e8fd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e065e9a8be55d35c22d560e6349055e42404cb28","tid":102560,"uid":56757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T06:12:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前係高登睇到個爸打遊中東個post話，如果護照有以色列、巴基斯坦呢啲國家既入境記錄，好似有啲國家以後都入唔到，例如馬來西亞。<br />\n<br />\n真唔真？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以如果你係機場入境嘅話佢唔會吸印係你個passport到而係好似台灣咁比張Entry Permit你，佢地都知自己國家個印會有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e83e75d1f84b4bdc1caa8813e92aca91c640906","tid":102560,"uid":49727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T06:14:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前係高登睇到個爸打遊中東個post話，如果護照有以色列、巴基斯坦呢啲國家既入境記錄，好似有啲國家以後都入唔到，例如馬來西亞。<br />\n<br />\n真唔真？</blockquote><br />\n換passport<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有啲國家係比國民同時有幾本passport<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （德國好似得）"},{"pid":"c1bc662b9ca181bbbce5a83d51de370f1f5e8727","tid":102560,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T06:15:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我本護照去過d回教國家，係唔係唔洗去？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同行有回教國家嘅同學連visa都唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></