 />\n<br />\n加利利海都okay, 各各他就反而無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇過海法又唔知有咩特別?<br />\n<br />\n巴打可唔可以推介下<br />\n<br />\n但巴打始終跟團, 有專車接送<br />\n<br />\n我就一個人去... 難去既地方只可以放棄<br />\n<br />\n根本唔可能睇得明希伯來文...<br />\n<br />\n同埋好驚俾人呃, 特別係睇遊記, 都有幾個話要好小心阿拉伯人, 即係班回教畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後...物價真係好撚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83590328f718be4734586aa355a7c2208e580a2a","tid":102560,"uid":19933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T13:34:34.000Z","msg":"巴打poly?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ede3d54ced2c33f58f54003e758f55cfad38627","tid":102560,"uid":43804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T13:38:56.000Z","msg":"留名睇相/遊記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}